name: SEED
description: SEED is a launch and growth engine designed to improve the success rate of new token launches. It provides a structured, end-to-end framework covering liquidity setup, stable-led KOL campaigns, market support, and user acquisition. SEED manages launch operations, protects early liquidity, and reinvests revenue into buybacks and ecosystem growth. The goal is to create sustainable post-launch performance rather than short-term spikes, giving projects a managed path from TGE through early traction.
